ction%20treatment%20next.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENostalgia%20sells%20%E2%80%94%20but%20not%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20is%20learning%20that%20lesson%20as%20it%20mines%20its%20library%20of%20iconic%20films%20for%20new%20versions.%20The%20Mouse%20House%20scored%20a%20win%20this%20past%20weekend%20with%20its%20live-action%20remake%20of%C2%A0%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flilo-and-stitch-box-office-disney-live-action-remakes-snow-white-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELilo%20%26amp%3B%20Stitch%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20shattered%20expectations%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmovie-theaters-are-having-their-best-memorial-day-weekend-ever-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecord-setting%20Memorial%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%20box%20office%20haul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'Lilo'%20will%20provide%20a%20blueprint%20for%20future%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20Comscore%20box-office%20analyst%20Paul%20Dergarabedian%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20He%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20got%20to%20be%20a%20corporate%20mandate%26quot%3B%20at%20Disney%20to%20dive%20into%20the%20vault%20in%20search%20of%20material%20for%20further%20remakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20one%20problem%20for%20Disney%3A%20It%20could%20be%20running%20out%20of%20compelling%20IP%20to%20give%20the%20live-action%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney's%20ill-fated%20reimagining%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-snow-white-opening-weekend-box-office-numbers-disapointment-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESnow%20White%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20earlier%20this%20year%20showed%20the%20perils%20of%20trying%20to%20remake%20a%20classic%20that%20contemporary%20audiences%20didn't%20connect%20to.%20And%20the%20company%20has%20already%20remade%20blockbusters%20like%20%26quot%3BBeauty%20and%20the%20Beast%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BAladdin%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3B