C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPaul%20Weiss's%20executive%20order%20imposed%20the%20same%20tailored%20process%20on%20its%20employees'%20security%20clearances%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20it%20took%20to%20escape%20that%20process%20%E2%80%94%20denouncing%20a%20former%20partner%2C%20changing%20client%20selection%20and%20hiring%20practices%2C%20and%20pledging%20pro%20bono%20work%20to%20the%20President's%20liking%20%E2%80%94%20had%20not%20even%20a%20glancing%20relationship%20to%20national%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2205f9b6a5-bd58-4a0b-9507-22f93db306d7%5C%22%3E4.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Founding%20Fathers%20knew%20this!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20District%20Judge%20Richard%20Leon's%20exclamation%20point-ridden%20order%20knocking%20down%20an%20executive%20order%20targeting%20WilmerHale%20quotes%20from%20Alexander%20Hamilton%20and%20the%20Federalist%20papers%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20an%20independent%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wasn't%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20Howell%20said%20in%20her%20earlier%20order%20that%20John%20Adams%20made%20the%20unpopular%20decision%20to%20represent%20British%20soldiers%20accused%20of%20murder%20for%20their%20roles%20in%20the%20Boston%20Massacre.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20American%20system%20of%20justice%20is%20an%20independent%20judiciary%20and%20an%20independent%20bar%20willing%20to%20tackle%20unpopular%20cases%2C%20however%20daunting%2C%26quot%3B%20Leon%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Founding%20Fathers%20knew%20this!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20executive%20orders%20violated%20those%20%26quot%3Bfundamental%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20concluded%20that%20this%20Order%20must%20be%20struck%20down%20in%20its%20entirety%20as%20unconstitutional%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BIndeed%2C%20to%20rule%20otherwise%20would%20be%20unfaithful%20to%20the%20judgment%20and%20vision%20of%20the%20Founding%20Fathers!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b55074a5-d09b-41aa-bac8-ec21412c2d6b%5C%22%3E5.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Order%20is%20akin%20to%20a%20gumbo%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELeon's%20gumbo%20metaphor%20is%2C%20once%20again%2C%20a%20spicy%20swipe%20at%20Paul%20Weiss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20arguments%20leading%20up%20to%20each%20decision%2C%20judges%20weighed%20whether%20to%20block%20the%20entirety%20of%20each%20of%20Trump's%20orders%20or%20allow%20some%20parts%20to%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20footnote%2C%20Leon%20broke%20down%20the%20five%20different%20sections%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwilmerhale-lawyers-security-clearances-trump-executive-orders-big-law-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20WilmerHale%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20compared%20them%20to%20gumbo%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Order%20is%20akin%20to%20a%20gumbo.%20Sections%202%20through%205%20are%20the%20meaty%20ingredients%20%E2%80%94%20e.g.%2C%20the%20Andouille%2C%20the%20okra%2C%20the%20tomatoes%2C%20the%20crab%2C%20the%20oysters%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BBut%20it%20is%20the%20roux%20%E2%80%94%20here%2C%20%C2%A71%20%E2%80%94%20which%20holds%20everything%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeon%20wrote%20that%20Trump%20rescinding%20Paul%20Weiss's%20order%20%26quot%3Bin%20full%26quot%3B%20after%20it%20struck%20a%20deal%20shows%20that%20he%20intended%20the%20orders%20%26quot%3Bto%20stand%20or%20fall%20as%20a%20whole.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20gumbo%20is%20served%20and%20eaten%20with%20all%20the%20ingredients%20together%2C%20and%20so%20too%20must%20the%20sections%20of%20the%20Order%20be%20addressed%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20also%20made%20clear%20that%20the%20gumbo%20is%20spicy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20explained%20in%20this%20Memorandum%20Opinion%2C%20this%20gumbo%20gives%20the%20Court%20heartburn%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-big-law-judge-decisions-quotes-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748505661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68375ba9c6ad288d14821807%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-big-law-judge-decisions-quotes-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Donald%20Trump's%20deal%20with%20Paul%20Weiss%20has%20backfired%20as%20judges%20say%20it%20shows%20Trump%20never%20had%20national%20security%20concerns%20about%20Big%20Law%20firms.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40businessinsider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-big-law-judge-decisions-quotes-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20lost%20my%20job%20to%20AI%2C%20but%20then%20used%20it%20to%20supercharge%20my%20search%20for%20a%20new%20role%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mark%20Quinn%20on%20a%20hike%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68371612c6ad288d148209e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221086%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Quinn%20used%20AI%20to%20level%20up%20his%20job%20search%20after%20losing%20his%20job%20to%20the%20technology.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Mark%20Quinn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMark%20Quinn%20was%20at%20a%20startup%20when%20GPT-4%20emerged%20and%20could%20do%20the%20work%20of%20the%20team%20he%20was%20building.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tech%20veteran%20had%20to%20wind%20down%20that%20operation%20before%20figuring%20out%20what%20he%20would%20do%20next.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20months%20without%20success%2C%20he%20turned%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-mistake-companies-make-bcg-tech-executive-2025-5%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20to%20help%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20job%20search.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMark%20Quinn%20is%20the%20senior%20director%20of%20AI%20operations%20for%20Pearl%2C%20an%20AI%20search%20platform%20for%20professional%20services.%20In%20a%20prior%20role%20at%20a%20startup%2C%20the%20arrival%20of%20OpenAI's%20GPT-4%20meant%20artificial%20intelligence%20could%20do%20the%20work%20of%20a%20team%20he%20was%20building.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20brevity%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20last%20job%2C%20I%20was%20at%20a%20startup.%20Before%20that%2C%20I%20was%20leading%20engineering%20operations%20at%20Waymo.%20It%20was%20a%203%2C000-person%20organization%2C%20a%20rocket%20ship%20all%20its%20own.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20my%20career%20was%20fairly%20well%20established%20and%20going%20well%20by%20most%20indications.%20So%2C%20when%20the%20startup%20came%20along%2C%20it%20was%20about%20this%20bigger%20swing%20and%20this%20even%20bigger%20opportunity%2C%20potentially%2C%20to%20help%20this%20company%20unlock%20what%20they%20were%20going%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20main%20role%20in%20that%20was%20to%20lead%20what%20was%20the%20primary%20human-in-the-loop%20operation%20responsible%20for%20supervising%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-replace-jobs-or-increase-worker-productivity-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecurating%20the%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20joined%2C%20it%20was%20already%20a%20500-person%20strong%20organization%2C%20and%20I%20was%20hired%20to%20ramp%20it%20to%20thousands.%20By%20all%20indications%2C%20we%20were%20doing%20the%20job%20really%20well.%20Then%20GPT-4%20came%20out.%20After%20playing%20with%20it%20for%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20months%2C%20we%20realized%20that%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20operation%20that%20I%20was%20scaling%2C%20really%20the%20entirety%20of%20it%2C%20was%20no%20longer%20needed.%20The%20technology%20had%20simply%20outpaced%20itself%20and%20the%20human%20in%20the%20loop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20spent%20my%20last%20few%20months%20there%20ramping%20that%20operation%20down%20and%20setting%20up%20a%20couple%20of%20other%20AI-related%20agents%20to%20help%20with%20things%20like%20quality%20technical%20writing.%20Once%20that%20was%20in%20place%2C%20my%20skills%20simply%20weren't%20needed%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20a%20super%20fun%20moment%2C%20and%20it%20was%20very%2C%20very%20bumpy.%20We%20had%20hundreds%20of%20people%20doing%20this%20work%20globally%2C%20so%20we%20had%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20ramp%20down%20those%20contracts%20as%20gracefully%20as%20possible%20to%20allow%20these%20folks%20to%20have%20time%20to%20hopefully%20get%20into%20other%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20team%20of%20about%2010%20people%2C%20only%20one%20person%20stayed%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22769c718d-93c4-49f4-96f7-215e430a7df2%5C%22%3E'Info%20workers%20beware'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20career%2C%20I'd%20gone%20from%20a%20place%20where%20companies%20like%20Waymo%2C%20Apple%2C%20and%20Amazon%20were%20coming%20to%20hire%20me%20to%20being%20out%20of%20a%20job%20and%20unable%20to%20get%20the%20attention%20of%20any%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20moment%20is%20making%20it%20such%20that%20these%20great%20companies%20now%20have%20way%20more%20capability%20and%20people%20than%20they%20may%20need.%20So%2C%20you've%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20great%20people%20that%20are%20now%20having%20to%20find%20their%20next%20play%2C%20but%20the%20next%20plays%20are%20dramatically%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%20hired%20at%20the%20startup%2C%20I%20spent%20the%20next%20four%20months%20with%20my%20team%20working%20tirelessly%20on%20basically%20solving%20this%20case%20and%20figuring%20out%20the%20right%20staffing%20and%20management%20model.%20Then%20GPT-4%20came%20out%2C%20and%20when%20I%20gave%20it%20the%20case%2C%20it%20was%20an%20epiphanal%20moment.%20It%20spit%20out%20the%20exact%20answer%20%E2%80%94%20the%20perfect%20answer%20%E2%80%94%20in%2030%20seconds%2C%20including%20what%20we%20thought%20were%20very%20clever%20adaptations%20that%20had%20taken%20us%20a%20week%20to%20identify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20not%20only%20gave%20us%20the%20answer%20but%20also%20the%20methods.%20I%20just%20sat%20there%20with%20my%20jaw%20in%20my%20hand.%20That%20was%20the%20moment%20that%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%2C%20%26quot%3BInfo%20workers%20beware.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f977fa88-7d25-4c57-8c16-1ea9ed33e146%5C%22%3EMy%20own%20pivot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20we%20began%20to%20wind%20down%20the%20operation%2C%20I%20started%20looking%20around%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20my%20next%20play%20would%20be.%20I%20spent%20about%20five%20months%20conducting%20my%20job%20search%20the%20wrong%20way%20and%20getting%20nowhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20this%20moment%20sitting%20there%2C%20again%2C%20with%20my%20jaw%20in%20my%20hand%2C%20wondering%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20am%20I%20doing%20wrong%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20came%20out%20of%20that%20moment%20of%20almost%20desperation%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI've%20asked%20everybody%20else.%20AI%2C%20what%20do%20you%20got%3F%26quot%3B%20It%20came%20back%20with%20more%20nuance%20and%20appreciation%20than%20I%20ever%20could%20have%20imagined.%20That's%20when%20I%20moved%20into%20collaboration%20mode%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20was%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-notebooklm-ai-podcast-tool-customize-feature-update-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20NotebookLM%3C%2Fa%3E.%20When%20it%20came%20out%2C%20people%20had%20fun%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20putting%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20into%20it%20and%20creating%20a%20podcast.%20I%20actually%20found%20incredible%20utility%20in%20doing%20that.%20It's%20interesting%20to%20drop%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20and%20your%20LinkedIn%20profile%20into%20NotebookLM%20and%20see%20what%20AI%20makes%20of%20your%20career.%20What%20does%20it%20call%20out%20as%20the%20highlights%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20did%20this%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20there%20were%20great%20things%20about%20my%20background%20and%20experiences%20that%20I%20wasn't%20telling%20people%20because%20I%20didn't%20see%20or%20appreciate%20them%2C%20but%20this%20podcast%20called%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20using%20AI%2C%20I%20wrote%20a%20nice%20cover%20letter%2C%20updated%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20and%20started%20looking%20around%20on%20LinkedIn%20and%20applying.%20I%20was%20using%20my%20network%2C%20casting%20the%20line.%20I%20wasn't%20just%20in%20a%20corner%20quietly%20hoping%20something%20would%20come%20to%20me%2C%20but%20it%20was%20the%20traditional%20approach%20of%2C%20%26quot%3BHere's%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20that%20I%20made%20for%20every%20job.%20Here's%20a%20cover%20letter%20with%20a%20few%20tweaks.%26quot%3B%20I%20was%20essentially%20cold%20applying%20and%20trying%20to%20hit%20people%20up%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20have%20probably%20heard%20that%20you%20should%20tailor%20your%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20cover%20letter%2C%20or%20communications%20for%20a%20role.%20But%20that's%20hard%20when%20you're%20in%20the%20grind%20and%20just%20trying%20to%20get%20a%20job.%20You've%20already%20applied%20to%20a%20bunch%2C%20and%20you're%20tired%20and%20don't%20want%20to%20stare%20at%20the%20same%20words%20again%20and%20again.%20This%20is%20where%20AI%20is%20extremely%20helpful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20created%20what%20I%20called%20JobHunt%20GPT.%20Now%20I've%20turned%20it%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchatgpt.com%2Fg%2Fg-683648602ea08191a73a5038962a1ef5-careerbuddy-gpt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECareerBuddy%20GPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20JobHunt%20GPT%20was%20what%20came%20out%20of%20all%20this%20exploration.%20In%20my%20case%2C%20it%20was%20a%20custom%20GPT%20that%20understood%20my%20background%2C%20where%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20go%2C%20and%20the%20history%20of%20the%20jobs%20I'd%20applied%20for.%20So%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20go%20to%20it%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20here's%20a%20new%20job.%20Can%20you%20assess%20my%20candidacy%20for%20this%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20I%20get%20is%20an%20objective%20review%20of%20how%20I%20mesh%20up%20against%20a%20role.%20Then%2C%20I%20can%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BAlright%2C%20pick%20apart%20my%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20What%20do%20I%20need%20to%20adjust%3F%26quot%3B%20It%20can%20generate%20the%20updated%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20focusing%20on%20the%20things%20that%20are%20important%20for%20the%20role.%20And%20it%20can%20write%20the%20cover%20letter%20and%20identify%20the%20key%20people%20for%20me%20to%20reach%20out%20to.%20It's%20essentially%20like%20lead%20analysis%20and%20lead%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20to%20anybody%20else%20would%20be%2C%20don't%20wait%20five%20months%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20right%20way%20to%20do%20it.%20The%20world%20has%20changed.%20This%20applies%20to%20anything%2C%20but%20especially%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20job%2C%20you%20have%20to%20leverage%20the%20most%20powerful%20tool%20available%2C%20which%20is%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20job%20hunt%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atparadis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Etparadis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-took-tech-worker-job-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748505601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68371640ca50259add4d2b95%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-took-tech-