erson%20Kush%20Desai%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20after%20the%20ruling%20was%20released%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20foreign%20countries'%20%26quot%3Bnonreciprocal%20treatment%20of%20the%20Unites%20States%20has%20fueled%20America's%20historic%20and%20persistent%20trade%20deficits.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20deficits%20have%20created%20a%20national%20emergency%20that%20has%20decimated%20American%20communities%2C%20left%20our%20workers%20behind%2C%20and%20weakened%20our%20defense%20industrial%20base%20%E2%80%94%20facts%20that%20the%20court%20did%20not%20dispute%2C%26quot%3B%20Desai's%20statement%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20for%20unelected%20judges%20to%20decide%20how%20to%20properly%20address%20a%20national%20emergency.%20President%20Trump%20pledged%20to%20put%20America%20First%2C%20and%20the%20Administration%20is%20committed%20to%20using%20every%20lever%20of%20executive%20power%20to%20address%20this%20crisis%20and%20restore%20American%20Greatness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lead%20plaintiffs%20in%20the%20case%2C%20Victor%20Schwartz%20and%20his%20daughter%20Chloe%20Schwartz%2C%20who%20own%20and%20run%20the%20New%20York-based%20specialty%20wine%20and%20spirits%20importing%20company%20VOS%20Selections%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20tariffs%20were%20catastrophic%20for%20their%20company.%20They%20dampened%20consumer%20sentiment%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmain-street-trump-trade-war-tariffs-small-businesses-impact-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edecreased%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%2016%25%20compared%20to%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImporting%20and%20sourcing%20things%20you%20don't%20find%20everywhere%2C%20I%20really%20thought%20that%20was%20going%20to%20be%20my%20edge%20in%20the%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Schwartz%2C%20whose%20small%20business%20sources%20around%20600%20types%20of%20wine%20and%20spirits%20from%20350%20different%20producers%20around%20the%20world.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20tariffs%20hit%20us%20in%20so%20many%20different%20ways.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIlya%20Somin%2C%20a%20lawyer%20on%20the%20case%20and%20a%20law%20professor%20at%20George%20Mason%20University%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Freason.com%2Fvolokh%2F2025%2F05%2F28%2Fwe-won-our-tariff-case%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReason%3C%2Fa%3E%20magazine%20and%20shared%20with%20BI%2C%20described%20the%20court's%20ruling%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20major%20victory%20in%20the%20legal%20battle%20against%20these%20harmful%20and%20illegal%20tariffs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20I%20have%20contended%20that%20the%20virtually%20limitless%20nature%20of%20the%20authority%20claimed%20by%20Trump%20is%20a%20key%20reason%20why%20courts%20must%20strike%20down%20the%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Somin.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20glad%20to%20see%20the%20CIT%20judges%20agreed%20with%20our%20argument%20on%20this%20point!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20that%20Trump's%20trade%20strategy%20contributed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcontinued-supply-chain-problems-despite-trump-trade-deal-china-experts-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprice%20instability%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretailers-small-businesses-react-trump-trade-tariffs-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esupply%20chain%20snarls%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Major%20brands%2C%20including%20Macy's%2C%20Walmart%2C%20and%20Shein%2C%20said%20the%20tariffs%20were%20pushing%20them%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-raising-prices-increases-trump-tariffs-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eraise%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20consumers.%20Logistics%20experts%20and%20shipping%20industry%20insiders%20said%20the%20effects%20were%