ia.com%2F308289%2Ffood-writers-compile-a-kitchen-of-ones-own-book-to-document-heirloom-family-indian-recipes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esit%20down%20with%20the%20mothers%20of%20Kerala%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20understand%20their%20kitchen%20secrets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20three%20years%20saw%20him%20traverse%20265%20homes%20and%2070%20toddy%20shops%20across%20Kerala%2C%20testing%20over%20800%20recipes.%20He%20and%20his%20friends%20feasted%20on%20home-cooked%20food%2C%20pored%20their%20heads%20over%20generation-old%20recipes%2C%20and%20got%20a%20front%20row%20seat%20to%20how%20ingredients%20were%20wielded%20in%20specific%20ways.%20He%20began%20to%20see%20how%20ingredients%20coalesce%20to%20dictate%20the%20anatomy%20of%20the%20dish%2C%20its%20quality%2C%20and%20the%20emotion%20that%20will%20come%20through%20while%20eating%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20experience%20textured%20chef%20Regi%E2%80%99s%20understanding%20of%20Kerala%20cuisine.%20Kappa%20Chakka%20Kandhari%20went%20on%20to%20become%20a%20success.%20Today%2C%20Chatti%20finds%20common%20ground%20with%20it%20in%20wanting%20to%20spotlight%20the%20same%20authentic%20culture%2C%20but%20Chatti%E2%80%99s%20genius%20lies%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F313740%2Fgoa-chef-avinash-martins-turns-ancestral-land-into-farm-to-table-venture-cest-lavi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecelebrating%20hyperlocal%20ingredients%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20slow-cooking%20techniques.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20allows%20the%20spices%20to%20come%20together%20in%20a%20perfect%20blend.%20It%20creates%20a%20well-balanced%20dish.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20is%20Chef%20Regi%E2%80%99s%20metric%20for%20success%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20guest%2C%20who%20has%20grown%20up%20in%20Kerala%2C%20comes%20to%20Chatti%20and%20feels%20that%20it%20resembles%20a%20%3Cem%3Etoddy%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshop%20experience%20that%20they%20have%20had%20back%20home%2C%20that%20makes%20me%20happy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concludes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%20Venkatesh%3B%20All%20pictures%20courtesy%20Chef%20Regi%20Mathew%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748334600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D439211%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20Chatti%20in%20New%20York%2C%20Chef%20Regi%20Mathew%20has%20created%20%E2%80%98touchings%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20bite-sized%20appetisers%20commonly%20seen%20across%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20toddy%20shops%2C%20cocktails%20and%20authentic%20Kerala%20specialties.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F439211%2Fchatti-in-new-york-toddy-shop-kerala-concept-by-chef-regi-mathew-of-kappa-chakka-kandhari-kerala-cuisine%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It%E2%80%99s%20Not%20Just%20the%20Rain%3A%20What%20Really%20Causes%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Monsoon%20Floods%20Every%20Year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPicture%20having%20a%20cup%20of%20%3Cem%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(tea)%20by%20the%20Marine%20Drive%20with%20the%20drizzle%20moistening%20your%20hair%2C%20the%20first%20raindrops%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F234921%2Fmumbai-rains-floods-how-to-stop-red-alert-water-damage-citizens-speak-solution-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMumbai%20monsoon%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20poetic.%20They%20tap%20against%20windows%2C%20soften%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20skyline%2C%20and%20bring%20respite%20from%20the%20torrid%20summer%20heat.%20But%20as%20the%20rain%20gathers%20strength%2C%20this%20poetry%20turns%20into%20panic.%20Roads%20disappear%20under%20water%2C%20trains%20grind%20to%20a%20ha